edu.wpi.cs.jburge.SEURAT.rationaleData
Class Association

java.lang.Object
  edu.wpi.cs.jburge.SEURAT.rationaleData.Association

public class Association
extends java.lang.Object

Contains the information associating an alternative with the code that implements it. This class is now saved and restored to the database and reflects the data elements in the database table. However, its from and toDatabase methods are not used in all database save/restore operations.

Author:
jburge
